title: Jim Carrey Serves as Pallbearer at Cathriona White's Funeral
text: Jim Carrey laid his late girlfriend Cathriona White to rest on Saturday (October 10) in her native Ireland. The 53-year-old actor served as a pallbearer, someone who helps carry the casket from the church, following the funeral services. Jim joined Cathriona‘s family at her hometown church in Cappawhite for the Reqiuem Mass. After the service, [...] »
